# Client quotation sites

Skill: [`.cursor/skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md`](../skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md)  
**Catalog:** [`client-sites/README.md`](../../client-sites/README.md)

## Systems-first previews

Each client demo is **website + browsable admin system** on one Netlify host:

- Admin demo (pre-logged-in, multi-page nav): `/admin/` ‚Äî **shown first** in portfolio preview
- Marketing site: `/`
- Portfolio `?preview={slug}` ‚Üí **4 panels:** admin desktop/mobile **first**, then site desktop/mobile

Pricing: **‚Ç±15k / ‚Ç±18k = website only**. Admin in the preview is a **sample**; a production business system is **priced separately**. Say this in every outreach email/SMS/messenger. Cadence remains **`3d1w`** (3d ‚Üí 7d √ó 3, max 4).

## Per-client customization (mandatory)

Before deploy or outreach, customize **every** client admin demo:

- **`brand-config.js`** ‚Äî real business name, colors, logo (no ‚ÄúBusiness Admin‚Äù leftovers)
- **`demo-data.override.js`** ‚Äî client-specific packages, rates, names (not unchanged vertical pack defaults)
- **`system.painHero`** in `client.json` ‚Äî one-line pain for dashboard hero + outreach hook
- **Outreach drafts** ‚Äî systems-first; open with admin hook + pain, then browse admin, then website

**Do not** ship default pack text unchanged.

