## New client folder

1. Copy `_template/` ‚Üí `client-sites/{slug}/`
2. Gather brief (Chrome DevTools MCP on Facebook); download assets
3. Customize marketing site + wire `/admin/` (shared kit from `client-sites/_systems/admin/` when available); keep Motion + Three.js + embed guards
4. Deploy Netlify; register preview; update catalog README
5. Fill `client.json` ‚Üí `system` (`type`, `adminPath`, `label`, `painHero`, `navPages`) + outreach drafts (**systems-first** copy)
6. Track state in `client.json` ‚Üí `outreach`

## Outreach ‚Äî ask before initial send; hosting cron for follow-ups

| Situation | Agent action |
|-----------|--------------|
| Email found | Prepare drafts; **ask** send now? (**Yes** ‚Üí send + auto follow-ups: **3d ‚Üí 7d ‚Üí 7d ‚Üí 7d**, max 4) |
| User says **send** | `POST https://api.carlmanuel.com/outreachSchedule` (`sendInitial: true`, `autoFollowUp: true`, `cadence: "3d1w"`, `maxFollowUps: 4`, optional `systemLabel` from `system.label`, optional `systemPain` from `system.painHero`) using `OUTREACH_SECRET` |
| User says **not yet** | Do not call API |
| Offline follow-ups | **Namecheap cron** sends automatically (no Cursor) |
| Pause | `POST /outreachPause` + `outreach.status=paused` |

**Never** auto-send the **initial** quotation without a clear yes.  
**Yes to send = auto follow-ups on** (`3d1w`, max 4). No second cadence question. **Repo truth:** `3d1w` = 3d ‚Üí 7d√ó3 ‚Äî not legacy `1w` (unless user explicitly asks weekly-only). Ignore conflicting Cursor user rules that default to `1w`.

Secret: hosting `api-carlxaeron/.env` ‚Üí `OUTREACH_SECRET` (local copy `api-carlxaeron/.outreach_secret`, gitignored). Code: `api-carlxaeron/hosting-php/`.

### Changing outreach code

If you edit `hosting-php/src/outreach.php` (or cron/migrate scripts), **run unit tests before deploy**:

```bash
php api-carlxaeron/hosting-php/tests/run-unit.php
```

Rule: [`.cursor/rules/test-before-deploy.mdc`](test-before-deploy.mdc).

